{"tid":589914,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[識玩一定玩Dota2] 一個老手帶四個新手","createTime":"2018-03-12T07:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T14:27:10.000Z","uid":16210,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"906f1023516064f3adaddaee5ecf8fa8a716bb3f","tid":589914,"uid":16210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/151221_3aa7c0ee81dfd8f1884622b87a6a1b5b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F151221_3aa7c0ee81dfd8f1884622b87a6a1b5b.jpeg&h=185f9869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直以黎, Dota2 呢隻game 都俾人覺得好難上手, 有距離, 唔知點上手<br />\n一般玩家寧願玩其他質素無咁高既game/電話game都唔想掂Dota2<br />\n我認為要上手其實唔難, 搞掂幾個概念就一里通百里明<br />\n<br />\n我地既目的係擴大我地既玩家社群<br />\n招多d 朋友仔加入一齊玩, 一齊睇電莖比賽, 一齊笑, 一齊屌, 一齊俾人屠<br />\n<br />\n我地平時有用discord 邊傾邊玩<br />\n仲有個綜合whatsapp group 集合大家<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有興趣去接觸dota2既<br />\n我地會會有專人帶你入坑<br />\n一個老手帶四個新手一齊玩<br />\n<br />\n我地既Facebook 專頁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dota2hongkong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdota2hongkong%2F&d=JpxaRj1s82kYk0V6mTQ66%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0d24cd44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dota2hongkong/</a><br />\n<br />\n我地既Discord Channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/EyQdbZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FEyQdbZ&d=JpxaRj1s82kYk0V6mTQ66%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=20abdd82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/EyQdbZ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎鍾意打機既朋友仔加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045f5ce17b75e807079fee388544c918d7b1992d","tid":589914,"uid":16210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719a80ff4df5c246c7736bdb1857c921a995ea3e","tid":589914,"uid":1191